verbs.description: iaaf delays testosterone rules until semenya case verdict the [V: governing] [ARG0: body] of track and field will not apply rules to limit natural testosterone levels in female runners until the court of arbitration for sport concludes an appeal case brought by olympic champion caster semenya the iaaf said tuesday it agreed to postpone the intended nov 1 start for eligibility rules until cas gives a verdict expected on or before march 26 that target date is six months and two days before the start of the 2019 world championships in doha qatar london ontario qatar court of arbitration caster semenya testosterone doha south africa international association of athletics federations stephane bermon iaaf london monaco sport caster semenya
